kreogist-mu (1.0.0~beta5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Support for saving the last played state.
  * Support to change the application fonts.
  * Support to change the backend buffer length.
  * Support to delay the search operation for less searching.
  * Support the global short cut for Windows and macOS.
  * Support to minimized to tray icon.
  * Support to select the output audio device.
  * Support to change the volume up and down button level.
  * Support for MPV backend changing the audio settings.
  * Support for disabling the automatically playing the next song at the normal mode.
  * Improved the close event on low performance machine.
  * Fixed the FFMpeg analysiser might set empty string bug.
  * Fixed the potential bug when switching the music tab too fast.
  * Fixed the automatically online lyrics is not correct bug.
  * Fixed the lyrics download dialog scaling bug.
  * Fixed the main window position restore when minimized might be incorrect bug.
  * Fixed the Netease backend might stucked the queue bug.

